rope\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 353}, {\"ngram\": \"the 80s\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 377}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"teenagers\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It took 38 years for BMX racers to take to the skies of theOlympic Games, and since its introduction in Beijing in 2008, it's been a must-watch event.\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 597, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 468, \"end\": 471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.6446552528954853e-13, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}, {\"begin\": 551, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0740283086539577e-15, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"38 years\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 463}, {\"ngram\": \"the skies\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 499}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympic Games\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 519}, {\"ngram\": \"its introduction\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 547}, {\"ngram\": \"a must-watch event\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 596}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eight of the best riders, men and women, will line up at the gate and wait for the lights to go out before racing down an 8m-high, 35-degree start hill while reaching speeds as high as 60km/h, putting their bodies on the line to fight for the right to be crowned Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best riders\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 627}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"the gate\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 663}, {\"ngram\": \"the lights\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\"