": 2061, \"to\": 2100, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Alise Willoughby [the] world champion\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's kind of on point right now.\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2134, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"point\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was hard [Thursday] - we did not have any splits on the track so it's kind of hard to see how she compares to some of the others besides the lap times.\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any splits\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2186}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"the others\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2266}, {\"ngram\": \"the lap times\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But we are kind of banking on Elise getting a medal,\\\" USA Cycling High-Performance Director Staff MBE, a BMX Racing legend and 2008 Team GB Olympic gold medalist in the Track Cycling Team Sprint alongside Sir Chris Hoy, Sir Jason Kenny, toldExpress Sport.\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2388, \"end\": 2391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_the_British_Empire\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.536246309813949e-14, \"text\": \"MBE\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_the_British_Empire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_the_British_Empire\"}, {\"begin\": 2395, \"end\": 2398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.6446552528954853e-13, \"text\": \"BMX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BMX\"}, {\"begin\": 2465, \"end\": 2472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999995588951, \"rank\": 4.1319371697635255e-10, \"text\": \"Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource